  <DNP.World.FieldSummary>World summary</DNP.World.FieldSummary>
  <DNP.World.HintSummary>Describe the world in a few paragraphs. This is what the AI reads to understand where the story takes place.</DNP.World.HintSummary>
  <DNP.World.FieldHistory>History and lore</DNP.World.FieldHistory>
