  <DNP.World.FieldLocations>Notable locations</DNP.World.FieldLocations>
  <DNP.World.HintLocations>Places the party can visit. e.g. "The Sunken Archive: a flooded library with records from before the war."</DNP.World.HintLocations>
  <DNP.World.FieldRules>World rules</DNP.World.FieldRules>
  <DNP.World.HintRules>What exists and what doesn't. e.g. "Magic is outlawed. Technology is pre-industrial. The gods exist but keep silent."</DNP.World.HintRules>

  <!-- Campaign tab fields -->
  <DNP.World.CampaignExplainer>The campaign objective is the long-term goal that gives direction to each session. Players work toward it across multiple sessions. It can be as simple or complex as you like.</DNP.World.CampaignExplainer>
  <DNP.World.FieldCampaignName>Campaign name</DNP.World.FieldCampaignName>
  <DNP.World.HintCampaignName>e.g. "The Long Night", "Project Exodus"...</DNP.World.HintCampaignName>
  <DNP.World.FieldObjective>Campaign objective</DNP.World.FieldObjective>
  <DNP.World.HintObjective>What are the players trying to achieve? This is shown to the AI as the overall goal.\ne.g. "Find and destroy the signal tower before the raiders use it to call reinforcements."</DNP.World.HintObjective>
  <DNP.World.FieldDMNotes>DM notes (private)</DNP.World.FieldDMNotes>
  <DNP.World.HintDMNotes>Your private planning notes. NOT sent to the AI. Use them for session planning, secret plots, character motivations...</DNP.World.HintDMNotes>

  <!-- AI Config tab -->
  <DNP.World.AIExplainer>These instructions are sent directly to the narrator AI before each response. Use them to control style, length, content restrictions or anything else. The AI will follow them as closely as possible.</DNP.World.AIExplainer>
  <DNP.World.AIPresets>QUICK PRESETS (click to add)</DNP.World.AIPresets>
  <DNP.World.PresetShort>Short responses</DNP.World.PresetShort>
  <DNP.World.PresetShortText>Keep all responses under 3 sentences. Be concise.</DNP.World.PresetShortText>
  <DNP.World.PresetCinematic>Cinematic</DNP.World.PresetCinematic>
  <DNP.World.PresetCinematicText>Write in a cinematic and dramatic style. Use vivid descriptions of action and environment.</DNP.World.PresetCinematicText>
  <DNP.World.PresetDark>Dark tone</DNP.World.PresetDark>
  <DNP.World.PresetDarkText>Maintain a serious and grim tone. Death and failure are real consequences. No comic relief.</DNP.World.PresetDarkText>
  <DNP.World.PresetNoMeta>No meta-commentary</DNP.World.PresetNoMeta>
  <DNP.World.PresetNoMetaText>Never break the fourth wall. Never reference dice rolls, game mechanics, or the fact that this is a game.</DNP.World.PresetNoMetaText>
  <DNP.World.PresetSpanish>Spanish</DNP.World.PresetSpanish>
  <DNP.World.PresetSpanishText>Always respond in Spanish. Narrate in Spanish regardless of input language.</DNP.World.PresetSpanishText>
  <DNP.World.PresetClear>Clear</DNP.World.PresetClear>
  <DNP.World.FieldAIInstructions>Narrator AI instructions</DNP.World.FieldAIInstructions>
  <DNP.World.HintAIInstructions>Write whatever you want here. This goes directly to the AI system prompt.</DNP.World.HintAIInstructions>
  <DNP.World.PreviewLabel>FULL CONTEXT PREVIEW (what the AI will receive)</DNP.World.PreviewLabel>
